# Bulky_MVC

Bulky_MVC is an ASP.NET MVC application designed to manage books and categories with CRUD functionality.

## Features
- ASP.NET MVC Framework
- Entity Framework Core for database operations
- CRUD Operations
- Bootstrap for UI Styling

